title: Ep. - 332 - DREW SIDORA FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF ATLANTA KATE CHASTAIN REVIEWS THE BACHELOR
description:
Drew Sidora is the newest Real Housewife of Atlanta, and opens up about her career, joining the show, and what happened the night of the Bachelorette party in Isle of Palm.

 

Kate Chastain from Bravo’s Below Deck review an episode of ABC’s The Bachelor.
